highlights.text: Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Top Songs Singapore. “Tears” is the highest at #14.
“你，好不好？ - TVBS連續劇【遺憾拼圖】片尾曲” by Eric Chou has been on Top Songs Singapore the longest, at 454 weeks straight.
“Tears” by Sabrina Carpenter is the highest new entry on Top Songs Singapore at #14.
“Night Changes” by One Direction is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Singapore, up 76 spots at #105.
